Authentication :- 
It identifies the user and confirms that they are who they say they are..
TYPES:-
i) HTML FORM-based authentication
ii) Multi-factor mech
iii) windows integrated auth using NTLM or kerbereos
iv) remote authentication

=> Auth vulnerabalities arises from insecure implementation of the auth mech in an app

Weak pass requirements :-
Having no or minimal control over the quality of passwords that user's choose.
=> very short or blank
=> common dictionary words or names
=> pass is same as the username
=> use of default pass
=> missing or inadequate mfa

